p:
Chemical composition. Essential oil (thymol and carvacrol as the major components) (
 Pino et al., 1990; 
 Arumugam et al., 2016); phenolic compounds (e.g., rosmarinic, caffeic, gallic and 
 p-coumaric acids; quercetin derivatives; luteolin) (
 Brieskorn and Riedel, 1977b; 
 Arumugam et al., 2016), terpenoids and steroids (e.g., β-sitosterol, α-amyrin, stigmasterol) (
 Brieskorn and Riedel, 1977a; 
 Risch et al., 2012).
